{"tid":878951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來氮氣/氦氣自殺都好吸引","createTime":"2018-10-27T14:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T16:26:54.000Z","uid":37537,"like":20,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"817812e938eb4499be97cfe70a44aad1fccae2ab","tid":878951,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"吸一兩啖就可以昏迷<br />\n吸7分鐘腦幹死亡<br />\n<br />\n人窒息時的痛苦來自二氧化碳濃度提升<br />\n而因為呢種方法唔會提升體內二氧化碳濃度,過程理論上無痛苦<br />\n<br />\n係加拿大同美國已經好多人用呢種方法<br />\n死刑都用緊呢種方法了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inert_gas_asphyxiation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FInert_gas_asphyxiation&d=vBTfQxO9OeUepJqlu6n2%2F%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cd7c4fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inert_gas_asphyxiation</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------分隔線:以下內容與標題無關--------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n氦氣淘寶/amazon都有得買<br />\n而氮氣係phy / eng / chem / bio lab都好常見<br />\n大學實有<br />\n而家明白到原來氮氣都幾危險,尤其係例如LIFT呢類密閉空間"},{"pid":"a90bee122662e9dc1a69ea6af4dd8e51af686845","tid":878951,"uid":171816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a8808c5dc2e219959bded5ddfb663b9c37346","tid":878951,"uid":207182,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"雖然自殺係唔好 但無痛苦呢個論點我認同"},{"pid":"9e267b243a40a62017a5e58d409432837d8520e3","tid":878951,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"報驚"},{"pid":"5717c0dbe071cb5935498a19e3642323fdb75fc0","tid":878951,"uid":37537,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"當一個人想自殺<br />\n畀差佬拉應該會更鼓勵佢去自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6525800840c1f7a9e016a3